lds-antennas", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>All the nodes around my part of Newcastle have SF=11. Not sure why? Can&#39;t reach them in any case; working through the problems in <span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\">#node-builds-antennas</span></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/691585511948681266/158c8687ed967b7de3c557a5f77a09c6.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=hesit8or0149>Hesit8or</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1345305035902418985')\"> The default LoRa settings for Australia are \n915.8 MHz\nSF 10\nCR 5 \nBW 250Khz. </span> <span class=chatlog__reply-edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, March 1, 2025 3:02 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1427424261982650571", "author": "Garth (VK2TTY)", "author_handle": "garthk", "user_id": "145497997063487488", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/145497997063487488/432c533a05718217cf494e34a09712ef.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, October 13, 2025 6:34 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-13 6:34 p.m.", "text": "I'm willing to buy a couple repeaters and put them wherever helps. What's your BOM? From here, I should be able to reach most of the Waratah West valley up to that side of the university, plus a NW to NE triangle from there through to Tomago. Can't hit the cluster of nodes around the repeater in Waratah. Not sure I can reach the repeater in Birmingham Hills. (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;m willing to buy a couple repeaters and put them wherever helps. What&#39;s your BOM?\n\nFrom here, I should be able to reach most of the Waratah West valley up to that side of the university, plus a NW to NE triangle from there through to Tomago. Can&#39;t hit the cluster of nodes around the repeater in Waratah. Not sure I can reach the repeater in Birmingham Hills.</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Monday, October 13, 2025 6:35 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/691585511948681266/158c8687ed967b7de3c557a5f77a09c6.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=hesit8or0149>Hesit8or</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1346386324680085526')\"> Another 4 Repeaters ready to deploy </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1427590846789976108", "author": "ozcleric", "author_handle": "ozcleric_66577", "user_id": "1208898043102109739", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1208898043102109739/af39a69058d14bae9162671f35acde14.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, October 14, 2025 5:36 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-14 5:36 a.m.", "text": "we are running SF11 in Sydney and are very close to connecting Newcastle up", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>we are running SF11 in Sydney and are very close to connecting Newcastle up</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/145497997063487488/432c533a05718217cf494e34a09712ef.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=garthk>Garth (VK2TTY)</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1427420485393580166')\"> All the nodes around my part of Newcastle have SF=11. Not sure why? Can&#39;t reach them in any case; working through the problems in <span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\">#node-builds-antennas</span> </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1427601146968670322", "author": "Garth (VK2TTY)", "author_handle": "garthk", "user_id": "145497997063487488", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/145497997063487488/432c533a05718217cf494e34a09712ef.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, October 14, 2025 6:17 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-14 6:17 a.m.", "text": "Aha, that'd explain the SF=11 I'm seeing on the map. Joined #test , #nsw , and #centralcoast on my T-Beam, and begged the bouncer to be let into the NSW Mesh disco.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Aha, that&#39;d explain the SF=11 I&#39;m seeing on the map. Joined <code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">#test</code>, <code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">#nsw</code>, and <code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">#centralcoast</code> on my T-Beam, and begged the bouncer to be let into the NSW Mesh disco.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1427602335928025189", "author": "ozcleric", "author_handle": "ozcleric_66577", "user_id": "1208898043102109739", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1208898043102109739/af39a69058d14bae9162671f35acde14.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, October 14, 2025 6:22 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-14 6:22 a.m.", "text": "I just let you into the discord", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I just let you into the discord</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=